<L>__{3.59 interior paul's room evening}
<A>__{later, a knock on paul's door. no response. jaden pushes the door open a crack, revealing paul lost and alone on his bed in a tiny sliver of light among infinite council house darkness. seen like this, the marks life has left on paul are obvious.}
