<P>__{(a whisper)}
<D>__{goin' out dad ok?}
<A>__{paul just frowns. he seems too tired to speak. he expresses `come back safely' in a way that is very hard to bear. jaden enters the room. he tucks his old man up in bed safe. then he leaves the room quietly and pulls the door shut safe. he goes downstairs and exits the house quietly. the ceramic christ on the cross in the hallway is silent.}
